SubjectBy-election - Nanaimo–Ladysmith
PrecisOrder directing that a WRIT OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancy in the House of Commons for the electoral district of Nanaimo–Ladysmith (British-Columbia), with polling to take place on May 6, 2019.
